Description: The Return from Egypt; the Infant Jesus walking between the Virgin and St Joseph, God and the Holy Spirit above in the sky; arched composition; after Peter Paul Rubens Engraving
Curator's comments: After the painting by Rubens (Rooses 183). Reproduces in reverse S. a Bolswert's engraving (see Schneevoogt 25.116).
Bibliographic references: Schneevoogt 1873 / Catalogue des estampes gravées d'après P.P.Rubens (26.119)
Subjects: return of the holy family from egypt
